507
00:37:08,306 --> 00:37:09,802
With cash.

508
00:37:28,487 --> 00:37:29,561
Nice bike.

509
00:37:39,215 --> 00:37:41,470
The wedding's at
2:30, Fernando.

510
00:37:44,716 --> 00:37:46,822
We just got confirmation
